<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Legal Notice — Tesflix</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Legal notice for Tesflix — an independent, community-made dashboard for Tesla's in-car browser. No affiliation with Tesla, Inc." />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" media="print" onload="this.media='all'" />
		<noscript><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" /></noscript>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div class="ambient" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="blob blob-1"></div>
			<div class="blob blob-2"></div>
			<div class="blob blob-3"></div>
		</div>

		<main>
			<header>
				<a href="/" class="back-link">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
					Back
				</a>
				<h1 class="page-title">Legal Notice</h1>
			</header>

			<div class="content-box">
				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>No affiliation with Tesla</h2>
					<p>Tesflix is an independent, community-made project and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or in any way connected to Tesla, Inc. The name "Tesla" and all related marks are trademarks of Tesla, Inc. Any reference to Tesla on this website is solely for descriptive purposes — to indicate that this dashboard is designed for use with Tesla vehicles' in-car browser.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>No affiliation with third-party services</h2>
					<p>The streaming services, music platforms, sports channels, gaming platforms, and any other third-party services shown or linked on this website are independent companies with no connection to Tesflix. All trademarks, logos, and brand names appearing on this site are the property of their respective owners and are used here solely for identification purposes.</p>
					<p>Tesflix does not have any commercial or contractual relationship with any of the services listed. Accessing those services through Tesflix is subject to each service's own terms and conditions.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>No warranties</h2>
					<p>Tesflix is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind. We make no guarantees that linked services will be accessible, functional, or available in your region. Tesflix does not host, stream, or reproduce any content from third-party platforms.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>Open source</h2>
					<p>Tesflix is an open-source project. The source code is freely available and can be self-hosted. Anyone using the self-hosted version does so under their own responsibility.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>Contact</h2>
					<p>For any legal enquiries, please reach out via <a href="https://crstian.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">crstian.me</a>.</p>
				</section>
			</div>

			<footer>
				<div class="footer-inner">
					<a href="https://github.com/crstian19/tesflix" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-github" aria-label="GitHub repository">
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.477 2 12c0 4.418 2.865 8.166 6.839 9.489.5.092.682-.217.682-.482 0-.237-.009-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.604-3.369-1.341-3.369-1.341-.454-1.154-1.11-1.462-1.11-1.462-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.03 1.531 1.03.892 1.529 2.341 1.087 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.11-4.555-4.943 0-1.091.39-1.984 1.029-2.683-.103-.253-.446-1.27.098-2.647 0 0 .84-.269 2.75 1.025A9.564 9.564 0 0 1 12 6.844a9.59 9.59 0 0 1 2.504.337c1.909-1.294 2.747-1.025 2.747-1.025.546 1.377.202 2.394.1 2.647.64.699 1.028 1.592 1.028 2.683 0 3.842-2.339 4.687-4.566 4.935.359.309.678.919.678 1.852 0 1.336-.012 2.415-.012 2.741 0 .267.18.578.688.48C19.138 20.163 22 16.418 22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10z"/></svg>
					</a>
					<span class="footer-sep">&mdash;</span>
					<span>Made with ❤️ by <a href="https://crstian.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-link">Crstian</a> from 🇪🇸</span>
					<span class="footer-sep">&mdash;</span>
					<span>Tesflix {new Date().getFullYear()}</span>
				</div>
			</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

	:root {
		--bg: #0A0A0F;
		--surface: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
		--border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		--text: #F8FAFC;
		--muted: #64748b;
		--red: #E50914;
	}

	body {
		background-color: var(--bg);
		color: var(--text);
		font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100dvh;
		-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	.ambient {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.blob {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(120px);
		opacity: 0.18;
	}

	.blob-1 { width: 600px; height: 600px; background: #E50914; top: -200px; left: -100px; }
	.blob-2 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: #312E81; bottom: -150px; right: -100px; }
	.blob-3 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: #0EA5E9; top: 40%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); opacity: 0.08; }

	main {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		max-width: 860px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem;
	}

	header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.back-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.3rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		transition: color 150ms ease;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.back-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

	.back-link svg {
		width: 16px;
		height: 16px;
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 1.75rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
	}

	.content-box {
		background: var(--surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.legal-section h2 {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		padding-left: 0.75rem;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
	}

	.legal-section p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		line-height: 1.75;
		color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.7);
	}

	.legal-section p + p {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
	}

	.inline-link {
		color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.85);
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-underline-offset: 3px;
		transition: color 150ms ease;
	}

	.inline-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

	footer {
		margin-top: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.footer-inner {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
	}

	.footer-sep { opacity: 0.3; }

	.footer-link {
		color: var(--muted);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 150ms ease;
	}

	.footer-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

	.footer-github {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		color: var(--muted);
		transition: color 150ms ease;
	}

	.footer-github:hover { color: var(--text); }
	.footer-github svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		main { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
		.content-box { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
	}
</style>
